                <fr:title text="Tensor products of distributive lattices">Tensor products of distributive lattices</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Construction</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A,B]]></fr:tex> be two <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>-algebras, i.e. with maps <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D \to  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D \to  B]]></fr:tex>. The <html:em>tensor product</html:em> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>, denoted as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A \otimes _D B]]></fr:tex>, is generated by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a \otimes  b]]></fr:tex> for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b \in  B]]></fr:tex>, subject to:
  <html:ol><html:li>The congruence specifies joins are bilinear in each variable,
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ a \otimes  0 \sim  0 \sim  0 \otimes  b ]]></fr:tex>
    and that 
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ (a \vee  a') \otimes  b \sim  a \otimes  b \vee  a' \otimes  b, \quad  a \otimes  (b \vee  b') \sim  a \otimes  b \vee  a \otimes  b'. ]]></fr:tex></html:li>
    <html:li>The meets are pointwise,
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ a \otimes  b \wedge  a' \otimes  b' \sim  aa' \otimes  bb'. ]]></fr:tex></html:li>
    <html:li>This tensor is distributive for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>,
    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ ad \otimes  b \sim  a \otimes  db. ]]></fr:tex></html:li></html:ol></html:p>
                <html:p>
  We also have two inclusions <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A \to  A \otimes _D B]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B \to  A \otimes _DB]]></fr:tex>, sending <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A,b\in  B]]></fr:tex> to 
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ a \mapsto  a \otimes  1, \quad  b \mapsto  1 \otimes  b. ]]></fr:tex>
  It is easy to verify these are distributive lattice morphisms.
</html:p>
